  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan <br /><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Ninneko Clan <br />Your lightning reflexes quicken further - you are always ready to jump into (or out of) action! You gain the following benefits;</p><ul><li>Increase your Dexterity score by 1, to a max of 20.</li><li>You gain expertise in Acrobatics. If you already have expertise, then you gain expertise in one Dexterity skill you are proficient in.</li><li>You gain a +1 bonus to initiative checks and cannot be surprised while you are conscious.</li><li>As a reaction, you can move up to 15 feet when an enemy ends its turn within 5 feet of you. This movement doesn't provoke opportunity attacks.</li></ul>",
